title: US romps to 6-1 win over Cuba in Olympic qualifying match
text:
> Sports US romps to 6-1 win over Cuba in Olympic qualifying match United States midfielder Emerson Hyndman (8) gets past Cuba defender Adrian Arturo Diz Pe during the first half of a CONCACAF men's Olympic qualifying soccer match Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Kansas City, Kan. (AP Photo/Charlie Riedel)
